<Title>Amendments of the Data Protection Act 2018</Title>
</TitleBlock><ScheduleBody><P1group><Title>Part 6 (enforcement) (other than Schedules 15 to 17)</Title><P1 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64" id="schedule-2-paragraph-64">
<Pnumber>64</Pnumber>
<P1para>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/1/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/1" id="schedule-2-paragraph-64-1">
<Pnumber>1</Pnumber>
<P2para><Text>Section 157 is amended as follows.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/2/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/2" id="schedule-2-paragraph-64-2">
<Pnumber>2</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>In subsection (1), for “GDPR” (in both places) substitute “UK GDPR”;</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/3/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/3" id="schedule-2-paragraph-64-3">
<Pnumber>3</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>In subsection (2)(a), omit “74,”.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/4/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/4" id="schedule-2-paragraph-64-4">
<Pnumber>4</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>In subsection (5), for “20 million Euros” (in both places) substitute “£17,500,000”.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/5/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/5" id="schedule-2-paragraph-64-5">
<Pnumber>5</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>In subsection (6), for “10 million Euros” (in both places) substitute “£8,700,000”.</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
<P2 DocumentURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/6/made" IdURI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/6" id="schedule-2-paragraph-64-6">
<Pnumber>6</Pnumber>
<P2para>
<Text>Omit subsection (7).</Text>
</P2para>
</P2>
</P1para>
</P1></P1group></ScheduleBody></Schedule></Schedules></Secondary></Legislation>